%N A342818 Length of the longest monochromatic arithmetic progressions of difference d in the Thue-Morse sequence (A010060).
%C A342818 a(n) is the largest l such that there exists k with t(k) = t(k+n) = t(k+2*n) = ... = t(k+(l-1)*n), where t(n) = A010060(n).
